1554	184	\N	2	SuccessStoryDetailComponent	"body"=>"<p><strong>Raleigh, N.C., November 13, 2013</strong> &mdash; <a href=\\"http://www.maxpoint.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\">MaxPoint</a>, the company that helps retailers and brands drive in-store sales with its innovative Digital Zip<sup>&reg;</sup> technology, announced today that it has ranked 9th on Deloitte&rsquo;s Technology Fast 500&trade;, a ranking of the fastest growing public and private technology, media, telecommunications, life sciences and clean technology companies in North America. In addition to its top 10 ranking, MaxPoint further distinguished itself within its industry category as the 2nd fastest growing Internet company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Technology Fast 500 award winners are selected based on percentage fiscal year revenue growth between 2008 and 2012. During that period, MaxPoint&rsquo;s revenue grew 31,723 percent as the company worked with retailers, brands and agencies to drive sales by reaching qualified consumers in the right neighborhoods with hyperlocal digital advertising.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MaxPoint&rsquo;s Digital Zip technology, which pinpoints the best neighborhoods for digital advertising campaigns, has fueled the company&rsquo;s steady growth since 2007. The unique hyperlocal approach to digital advertising bridges offline and online data to drive local demand, so advertisers can more effectively reach consumers at a local level by targeting the specific neighborhoods that most appeal to their brands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;We are pleased to be a Technology Fast 500 company,&rdquo; said Joe Epperson, CEO of MaxPoint. &ldquo;The ranking is confirmation of what we already know &ndash; that we&rsquo;re growing quickly because we are addressing the core needs of our customers in an increasingly complex advertising environment. We will continue to help the nation&rsquo;s top advertisers use their data to drive in-stores sales through innovative hyperlocal digital advertising solutions.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information, visit <a href=\\"http://www.deloitte.com/fast500\\" target=\\"_blank\\">www.deloitte.com/fast500</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>About MaxPoint </strong><br />\r\nMaxPoint uses hyperlocal intelligence to help retailers, brands, and agencies make smarter digital advertising decisions. The company&rsquo;s Digital Zip<sup>&reg;</sup> technology employs the latest in machine learning to pinpoint the neighborhoods of consumers most likely to purchase an advertiser&rsquo;s products and services at local stores. Trusted by 13 of the 15 most advertised US brands and all of the top US media agencies, MaxPoint is the only solution of its kind to offer hyperlocal precision at scale. For more information, visit <a href=\\"http://www.maxpoint.com/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">www.maxpoint.com</a>, follow MaxPoint on Twitter <a href=\\"https://twitter.com/maxpoint_int\\" target=\\"_blank\\">@maxpoint_int</a>, and subscribe to the <a href=\\"http://maxpoint.com/onpoint-blog/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">OnPoint Blog</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Contact:</strong><br />\r\nKatie Sullivan<br />\r\nfama PR<br />\r\n617-986-5031<br />\r\n<a href=\\"mailto:maxpoint@famapr.com\\">maxpoint@famapr.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Top 10 List</strong><br />\r\n<img alt=\\"The Top 10 List\\" src=\\"/system/editor/W1siZiIsIjIwMTMvMTEvMTMvMDlfMzhfMzlfODM4X1RoZV9Ub3BfMTAucG5nIl0sWyJwIiwidGh1bWIiLCI4MDB4ODAwPiJdXQ/The%20Top%2010.png\\" style=\\"border-style:solid; border-width:0px; height:250px; margin:0px; width:800px\\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Top 10 List by Industry - Internet</strong><br />\r\n<img alt=\\"The Top 10 Interent List\\" src=\\"/system/editor/W1siZiIsIjIwMTMvMTEvMTMvMDlfMzhfNTJfOTA2X1RoZV9Ub3BfMTBfSW50ZXJuZXQucG5nIl0sWyJwIiwidGh1bWIiLCI4MDB4ODAwPiJdXQ/The%20Top%2010%20Internet.png\\" style=\\"border-style:solid; border-width:0px; height:270px; margin:0px; width:800px\\" /></p>\r\n", "title"=>" MaxPoint Ranked 9th Fastest Growing Company in North America on Deloitte’s 2013 Technology Fast 500™", "sidebar_text"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_target"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_page_id"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_external_url"=>""	\N	2013-11-13 15:08:40.53032	2013-11-13 18:53:17.147889
