510	53	\N	3	SuccessStoryDetailComponent	"body"=>"<p><strong>Goal: </strong>Increase awareness of the grocer&rsquo;s new pricing strategy to consumers in regional markets near its stores.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Strategy</strong><strong>:</strong> MaxPoint targeted digital ads in only relevant neighborhoods near stores where TV and newspaper ad buys were too expensive and/or inefficient.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Results: </strong>MaxPoint&rsquo;s solution eliminated 85% of impressions that would have been wasted with TV ads in two specific DMAs. The campaigns saved the retailer significant costs and increased its reach as digital is at most one-tenth the cost of newspaper advertising and reaches an ever-increasing audience in terms of size and demos. The grocer continues to renew with MaxPoint.&nbsp;</p>\r\n", "title"=>"How did a grocery retailer effectively expand market penetration in smaller, regional markets?", "pdf_uid"=>"2013/05/20/15_53_03_821_MaxPoint_Spotlight_Grocery_Retailer.pdf", "pdf_name"=>"MaxPoint Spotlight_Grocery Retailer.pdf", "sidebar_text"=>"", "header_image_uid"=>"2013/05/19/16_17_25_127_HeatMap_Schnucks_ChampaignIL2.png", "header_image_name"=>"HeatMap_Schnucks_ChampaignIL2.png", "sidebar_image_uid"=>"2013/05/17/12_32_33_690_Grocery_Aisle_Resized.jpg", "sidebar_image_name"=>"Grocery-Aisle-Resized.jpg", "sidebar_image_link_target"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_page_id"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_external_url"=>""	\N	2013-05-14 20:52:17.737558	2014-01-14 22:33:54.479579
