625	109	\N	2	SuccessStoryDetailComponent	"body"=>"<p>By Kristina Knight<br />\r\n<em>This article first appeared on BizReport.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>January 20, 2012</strong>&nbsp;<strong>&ndash; </strong>Recently&nbsp;<a href=\\"http://www.maxpoint.com/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">MaxPoint</a> surveyed attendees at the National Retail Federation&rsquo;s 101st Annual Convention &amp; Expo to learn how retailers plan to compete in 2012. Two of the top three responses to about mobile &ndash; using mobile to drive traffic and to create seamless shopping experiences. Other strategies included:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Using social media more effectively</li>\r\n\t<li>Create a cross-channel experience for shoppers</li>\r\n\t<li>Simplify check-outs and implementing mobile POS stations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nBut several responses were about the customer experience &ndash; creating a better customer experience online and in-store, using interactive displays and options in-store to drive engagement and to involve more technology in the shopping process.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\\"http://maxpoint.com/us/advertising-tips-and-strategies/advertising-insights/101-rules\\" target=\\"_blank\\"><strong>You can read the full report here</strong></a><strong>.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nCustomer experience, by the way, is the sticking point of a new suite of tools from Monetate. Called the Agility Suite, the tools are aimed at creating a better &ndash; read more personal &ndash; online customer experience. Through Agility Suite brands can test multiple campaigns to determine engagement level, can target consumers using real time data and in-session behaviors.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;The number one challenge we hear from CMOs is finding technology that really does rapidly improve their customers&rsquo; experience online,&rdquo; said Monetate founder and CEO David Brussin. &ldquo;Monetate&rsquo;s Agility Suite was designed to meet this need. It provides very targeted marketing solutions that work together in one comprehensive suite of products.&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPerhaps the most interesting of the tools, though, is Monetate Touchpoints. Through this tool brands can ensure that the brand message remains consistent across screens and channels so that consumers are &lsquo;promised&rsquo; one thing and given another.</p>\r\n", "title"=>"Tool to create more personalized experience online", "sidebar_text"=>"", "sidebar_image_uid"=>NULL, "sidebar_image_name"=>NULL, "sidebar_image_link_target"=>"_blank", "sidebar_image_link_page_id"=>"-1", "sidebar_image_link_external_url"=>"http://www.bizreport.com/"	\N	2013-05-15 00:27:35.752399	2013-08-27 20:30:50.817992
