686	127	\N	2	SuccessStoryDetailComponent	"body"=>"<p><strong>VP, Software Engineering</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nEddie joins MaxPoint from CA Technologies/NetQoS. At NetQoS, he grew the engineering team from 5 to 50+, leading the company to a profitable enterprise that was acquired by CA Technologies. Previously, Eddie held engineering leadership positions at SensAble, Eastman Kodak, and Intergraph. Eddie has a BA in music and a BS in mathematics and computer science from Jacksonville State University, as well as an MA in mathematics from the University of Alabama. Eddie not only plays the saxophone but also arranges musical scores that are played around the United States. In high school, famous saxophonist Sigurd Rascher gave a class. Eddie helped him finish up by standing on his chest to demonstrate breath support. Eddie was worried that he would either kill Sigurd or leave chewing gum on his shirt from his shoe. Much to his relief, he did neither.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><u><a href=\\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=1364515&amp;authType=name&amp;authToken=W24O&amp;locale=en_U\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\" target=\\"_blank\\">See LinkedIn profile</a></u></strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n", "title"=>"Eddie Jennings ", "sidebar_text"=>"", "header_image_uid"=>NULL, "header_image_name"=>NULL, "sidebar_image_uid"=>"2013/05/16/16_07_46_304_Leadership_Detail_643x416_Eddie.jpg", "sidebar_image_name"=>"Leadership_Detail_643x416_Eddie.jpg", "sidebar_image_link_target"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_page_id"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_external_url"=>""	\N	2013-05-15 06:05:24.832767	2013-07-17 18:43:33.183775
