1636	195	\N	3	SuccessStoryDetailComponent	"body"=>"<p><strong>Goal:</strong> Drive sales of U by Kotex at a national mass merchandiser through a coupon and sweepstakes offer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Strategy:</strong> MaxPoint used its Digital Zip<sup>&reg;</sup> technology to target neighborhoods that over-indexed for females ages 18&ndash;22 with an interest in fashion. Neighborhoods within six to eight miles of the mass merchandiser that met the audience profile were served digital ads for U by Kotex. Display ads boosted microsite traffic by offering a U by Kotex coupon in exchange for completing a personality quiz and by promoting a shopping sweepstakes contest for the national mass merchandiser.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Results:</strong> By using MaxPoint&rsquo;s hyperlocal digital advertising solution, U by Kotex experienced 3.5 times more microsite coupon prints weekly during the campaign. Average weekly sales increased 22% through the two weeks after the campaign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>U by Kotex is a registered trademark of Kimberly-Clark Corporation.</em></p>\r\n", "title"=>"\vMaxPoint Helps U by Kotex® Boost Sales by 22%", "pdf_uid"=>"2013/12/23/15_50_49_119_MaxPoint_Spotlight_Feminine_Care_Product_National_Mass_Merchandiser.pdf", "pdf_name"=>"MaxPoint Spotlight_Feminine Care Product_National Mass Merchandiser.pdf", "sidebar_text"=>"", "header_image_uid"=>"2013/12/23/15_50_16_120_HeatMap_UbyKotexMerchandiser_Seattle_legendbottom_645x460.png", "header_image_name"=>"HeatMap_UbyKotexMerchandiser_Seattle_legendbottom_645x460.png", "sidebar_image_uid"=>"2014/01/14/15_38_27_675_Girl_on_Laptop_306x435.png", "sidebar_image_name"=>"Girl on Laptop_306x435.png", "sidebar_image_link_target"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_page_id"=>"", "sidebar_image_link_external_url"=>""	\N	2013-12-23 21:49:21.217616	2014-01-14 22:39:59.411933
