273	24	\N	7	BulletpointsComponent	"title"=>"WHY WORK AT MAXPOINT?", "footer_text"=>"", "header_text"=>"<p>Growth. Since we started in 2007, we&rsquo;ve seen tremendous growth&mdash;growth in our results, growth in the businesses we&rsquo;ve helped, and growth in our employees. When you work at the 9th fastest growing company in North America, you get to grow your technology career by working in a challenging, fast-paced environment that rewards intelligence and curiosity. We&rsquo;re at the forefront of digital advertising technology, and we credit our team with getting us here.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our Culture</strong><br />\r\nWe&rsquo;re passionate about what we do, and it comes across in our vibrant work-hard, play-hard atmosphere. Our team includes the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Three employees who speak more than three languages</li>\r\n\t<li>Seven employees who have completed at least one triathlon</li>\r\n\t<li>A coffee shop owner</li>\r\n\t<li>A badminton champion</li>\r\n\t<li>A cellist, drummer, saxophonist, and flutist</li>\r\n\t<li>A former jazz director for a dance company</li>\r\n\t<li>An Olympic 100- and 200-meter backstroke swimmer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nIn other words, when you work with MaxPoint, you&rsquo;re joining a group of high achievers who never rest. &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>What We Say</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&ldquo;I love the vibrant atmosphere here at MaxPoint!&nbsp;We tackle new challenges every day, and we never stop learning.&nbsp;It is an incredibly fun and exciting place to work.&rdquo; &mdash;Jenny, Account Manager &nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Working at MaxPoint means a few things: you work hard while gaining experience in a wide variety of online marketing tactics. You don&rsquo;t know where the last month went, you do know the difference between a South African and an Australian accent (or you find out), and you meet people who own multiple penguin costumes. You also learn that Austin, Texas, is home to the smartest engineers in the world, and you receive limo rides to great parties. Through all of this, shoes are optional.&rdquo; &mdash;William, Senior Applied Statistician</p>\r\n"	\N	2013-05-10 05:58:48.328061	2014-02-11 16:11:42.996693
