734	1	15	grocers-localize-digital-campaigns-and-reach-consumers-before-shopping-lists-are-born	Grocers: Localize Digital Campaigns and Reach Consumers Before Shopping Lists are Born	<p>A recent post in Progressive Grocer posed a great question, &ldquo;Are you as smart as your shoppers?&rdquo; In order to stay a step ahead and help influence the decision making process, Progressive Grocer pointed out that savvy grocers will make it their business to know what shoppers want before they come in store.</p>\r\n	<p>A recent post in <a href="http://www.progressivegrocer.com/" target="_blank">Progressive Grocer</a> posed a great question, &ldquo;Are you as smart as your shoppers?&rdquo;&nbsp; In order to stay a step ahead and help influence the decision making process, Progressive Grocer pointed out that savvy grocers will make it their business to know what shoppers want before they come in store. Let&rsquo;s expand. <!--more--><br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore than ever before, consumers are going online, whether it is through social networks, smartphones and/or tablets, to meet their shopper needs. According to a Deloitte&rsquo;s American Pantry study, 90% of shoppers know what they&rsquo;re buying before heading in-store and 75% of shoppers believe they are smarter shoppers than they were a year ago with the vast opportunities to complete research online. According to Jim Dudlicek, Senior Editor at Progressive Grocer, &ldquo;There&rsquo;s no reason that grocers &ndash; either on their own or in partnership with branded companies &ndash; shouldn&rsquo;t be reaching into their consumers&rsquo; kitchens to be there when shopping lists are born.&rdquo; Cue, localized digital advertising.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGrocers, fret no more. Reach shoppers before shopping lists are born with localized digital advertising. Precisely reach your audience online, within a specific store radius, and only deliver your digital ad when the audience meets the exact criteria of your shopper profile.&nbsp;