t a very granular level.&nbsp; <a href="http://www.maxpoint.com/us/digital-advertising-solutions" target="_blank">Localized targeting ad solutions</a> allow marketers to apply high accuracy targeting &ndash; getting local reach while maintaining national scale. In order to drive engagement and action with a campaign call to action or offer, digital ads need to be seen by the intended audience who will be receptive to the messaging.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>More opportunities for advertising creative:</strong> Traditional advertising methods can limit creative &ndash; however, online advertising provides advertisers with vast opportunities for campaign creative. For instance, advertisers can leverage displayand in-stream video formats to deliver campaigns.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs advertisers continue to allocate more offline ad dollars online, it is important to remain strategic about creating and delivering campaigns. Advertisers can deliver a strong marketing mix by leveraging &ldquo;cross-platform campaigns,&rdquo; but need to make sure they know what works and what to avoid. More on creating &ldquo;cross-platform&rdquo; campaigns <a href="http://maxpoint.com/us/digital-advertising-company/onpoint-blog/2012/5/9/creating-cross-platform-campaigns-what-works-what-to-avoid">here</a>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor more statistics on online advertising growth, click <a href="http://maxpoint.com/us/digital-advertising-company/onpoint-blog/2012/6/15/online-ad-spending-infographic" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>\r\n	t	2012-06-18 14:45:29	\N	2012-06-18 14:45:29	2013-09-20 00:32:53.208396	49	MaxPoint, MaxPoint Interactive, OnPoint, online advertising, online advertising spend, digital
